    'compliance.cl.desc': 'Chilean Ministry of Transport and MTT approval — certified for freight haulage across Chile\'s national highway network. Zero-emission classification confirmed for emission-restriction zone exemption.',
    'compliance.cl.name': 'Chile',
    'compliance.cn.desc': 'MIIT type approval and full GB/T national standard compliance under China\'s mandatory new energy vehicle framework — covering battery safety, charging, telematics, energy consumption, road safety, and dimensions.',
    'compliance.cn.name': 'China',
    'compliance.eu.desc': 'EU whole vehicle type approval under Regulation 2018/858 and all mandatory UNECE regulations — valid across all 27 EU member states plus Norway, Switzerland, and Iceland. Covers framework, braking, lighting (28 regulations), occupant protection, drivetrain, electrical safety, EMC, tyres, and advanced safety systems.',
    'compliance.eu.name': 'European Union',
    'compliance.h1': 'Windrose E670 — Compliance by Market',
    'compliance.intro': 'The Windrose E670 is fully homologated in Europe, the United States, China, and Chile. Below is a complete listing of the regulations, standards and type approvals met in each jurisdiction.',
