    'ev_realty_mcs.body.0': 'Kempower, Windrose, and EV Realty have successfully validated MCS (Megawatt Charging System) interoperability at EV Realty\'s San Bernardino Powered Properties truck hub.',
    'ev_realty_mcs.body.1': 'The test represents a critical milestone toward MCS commercialization for North American heavy-duty vehicles, demonstrating real-world megawatt-level charging capability.',
