    'missing.64': 'Driving Assistance',
    'missing.65': 'ACC is only a driver assistance system. The driver is responsible for safe driving.',
    'missing.66': 'ACC may not work properly in heavy traffic, roads with water or slush, heavy rain and snow, poor visibility, windy conditions, or driving on slopes.',
    'missing.67': 'The AEB system detects target vehicles or obstacles, predicts a risk of potential forward collision, sends a warning signal, and automatically applies brakes in emergency situations. Activate/deactivate via',
