    'antwerp_port_assembly.subline': 'Windrose establishes Windrose Park Antwerp along Noorderlaan — its first European electric truck assembly facility.',
    'antwerp_port_assembly.type': 'Press Release',
    'assembly.desc': 'Seven straightforward steps — any certified local partner, no specialist tooling required. Reduces logistics cost, creates local jobs, enables rapid market entry across 5 continents.',
