    'compliance.us.desc': 'Full FMVSS compliance under 49 CFR Part 571, complete EPA GHG and emissions compliance (ZEV exempt), and CARB ZEV/ACT/HVIP qualification — enabling operation and registration in all 50 states including California.',
    'compliance.us.name': 'United States',
    'engie_vianeo.body.0': 'ENGIE Vianeo and Windrose have joined forces to accelerate the electrification of heavy-duty vehicles across Europe, combining ENGIE\'s energy infrastructure expertise with Windrose\'s electric truck technology.',
