    'atc_2600km_netherlands_hungary.body.0': 'ATC Computer Transport & Logistics completed a landmark 2,600 km round trip from Venlo, Netherlands to Budapest, Hungary using a Windrose electric truck — proving that battery-electric trucks can match diesel on demanding cross-border European routes.',
