    'terawatt_partnership.body.0': 'Windrose and Terawatt Infrastructure have deepened their strategic partnership with live high-power charging demonstrations and full software integration at Terawatt facilities.',
    'terawatt_partnership.body.1': 'The partnership ensures Windrose trucks are fully compatible with Terawatt\'s growing US charging network, enabling seamless plug-and-charge experiences for fleet operators.',
