    'tja_portugal.body.0': 'Portuguese logistics operator TJA Transportes J. Amaral has trialled the Windrose long-haul electric truck, marking a key milestone in the electrification of freight transport on the Iberian Peninsula.',
    'tja_portugal.body.1': 'The trial demonstrates growing momentum for zero-emission freight across Southern Europe, following successful pilots in Spain with CEVA Logistics.',
    'tja_portugal.headline': 'TJA Transportes J. Amaral Tests Windrose Electric Truck in Portugal',
    'tja_portugal.stat_label.0': 'Electric',
