    'specs.overlap.desc': 'Each variant is homologated for its target market — but shares a high percentage of components with every other variant, minimising tooling investment and enabling global supply chain consolidation.',
    'specs.overlap.h2': 'Global parts overlap across variants',
    'specs.overlap.label': 'Platform Commonality',
