    'hubject_plug_charge.body.0': 'Windrose and Hubject have partnered to implement',
    'hubject_plug_charge.body.1': 'The integration supports both CCS and MCS charging standards, future-proofing Windrose trucks for next-generation charging infrastructure.',
    'hubject_plug_charge.headline': 'Hubject and Windrose Partner to Enable Plug&Charge and MCS',
